snippet.title: Sushant death: Rhea Chakraborty arrested by NCB in drugs case after questioning
snippet.description:
Actor Rhea Chakraborty was arrested by the Narcotics Control Bureau in a drugs case related to Sushant Singh Rajput's death. Her brother, Showik, and Sushant's house manager, Samuel Miranda, had been arrested days earlier by the NCB. The development came after 3 consecutive days of questioning of Rhea by NCB investigators. A day before her arrest, Rhea had filed a complaint with Mumbai police against Sushant's sister Priyanka Singh. The former had accused the latter of procuring a fake medical prescription for the late actor. Rhea alleged that within five days of Priyanka getting the prescription for anxiety medicines for Sushant, he died. The actor was found dead at his Mumbai residence on June 14. His father accused Rhea of abetting his suicide and siphoning off his assets. Watch the full video for more.

snippet.localized.title: Sushant death: Rhea Chakraborty arrested by NCB in drugs case after questioning
snippet.localized.description:
Actor Rhea Chakraborty was arrested by the Narcotics Control Bureau in a drugs case related to Sushant Singh Rajput's death. Her brother, Showik, and Sushant's house manager, Samuel Miranda, had been arrested days earlier by the NCB. The development came after 3 consecutive days of questioning of Rhea by NCB investigators. A day before her arrest, Rhea had filed a complaint with Mumbai police against Sushant's sister Priyanka Singh. The former had accused the latter of procuring a fake medical prescription for the late actor. Rhea alleged that within five days of Priyanka getting the prescription for anxiety medicines for Sushant, he died. The actor was found dead at his Mumbai residence on June 14. His father accused Rhea of abetting his suicide and siphoning off his assets. Watch the full video for more.

snippet.title: Dead by Daylight | Descend Beyond | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience the scourge of ambition with the Descend Beyond Chapter in Dead by Daylight. 

The Blight, a bright and ambitious chemist who sought to enhance humanity through the use of his compounds, only to become a victim of his own ambitions, is the new Killer. After his research was stolen, The Blight was lured into the Realm of the Entity by the promise of new, forbidden knowledge. The new survivor is Felix Richter, an eccentric architect with a unique vision. Returning to the mysterious island where his father had disappeared, Felix descended into the darkness beyond and was never seen again.   

DESCEND BEYOND Chapter is available now in Dead by Daylight. 

LEARN MORE ABOUT THE CHAPTER: https://deadbydaylight.com/en/chapters/descend-beyond 

BUY GAME: https://deadbydaylight.com/ 

Dead by Daylight is an asymmetrical multiplayer horror game where one player takes on the role of a brutal Killer and the other four play as Survivors. As a Killer, your goal is to sacrifice as many Survivors as possible. As a Survivor, your goal is to escape and avoid being caught and killed.  

Join the official forum: https://forum.deadbydaylight.com/en/  

Like and follow us on our official Social Media Channels:  
- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DeadByDaylight/  
- Twitter: https://twitter.com/deadbybhvr  
- Instagram: https://instagram.com/deadbydaylight

snippet.title: HEAT at BUCKS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | September 8, 2020
snippet.description:
HEAT at BUCKS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | September 8, 2020

Led by Jimmy Butler‚Äôs 17 PTS, 10 REB and 6 AST, the Miami Heat defeated the Milwaukee Bucks, 103-94, in Game 5. Additionally for the Heat, Tyler Herro recorded 14 PTS, 8 REB and 6 AST in the victory, while Khris Middleton tallied 23 PTS, 7 REB and 6 AST for the Bucks. After closing out this best-of-seven series, 4-1, the Heat will now advance to the Eastern Conference Finals for the first time since 2014 to face the winner of the Toronto Raptors ‚Äì Boston Celtics series (Boston currently leads, 3-2.)

snippet.title: Android 11 review: the most important settings
snippet.description:
Android 11 is officially here. It's out for Google Pixels and even some OnePlus phones. In this review, Dieter Bohn looks at the key settings you need to know to corral chat conversations, bubbles, location permissions, media controls, and the new power menu. The job of any mature OS is managing complexity and Android 11 just barely pulls it off.

Unfortunately for the Aggies, the storybook ending doesn't exactly work out for them.

snippet.title: Dead by Daylight | Descend Beyond | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience the scourge of ambition with the Descend Beyond Chapter in Dead by Daylight. 

The Blight, a bright and ambitious chemist who sought to enhance humanity through the use of his compounds, only to become a victim of his own ambitions, is the new Killer. After his research was stolen, The Blight was lured into the Realm of the Entity by the promise of new, forbidden knowledge. The new survivor is Felix Richter, an eccentric architect with a unique vision. Returning to the mysterious island where his father had disappeared, Felix descended into the darkness beyond and was never seen again.   

DESCEND BEYOND Chapter is available now in Dead by Daylight. 

LEARN MORE ABOUT THE CHAPTER: https://deadbydaylight.com/en/chapters/descend-beyond 

BUY GAME: https://deadbydaylight.com/ 

Dead by Daylight is an asymmetrical multiplayer horror game where one player takes on the role of a brutal Killer and the other four play as Survivors. As a Killer, your goal is to sacrifice as many Survivors as possible. As a Survivor, your goal is to escape and avoid being caught and killed.  

Join the official forum: https://forum.deadbydaylight.com/en/

Android 11 is officially here. It's out for Google Pixels and even some OnePlus phones. In this review, Dieter Bohn looks at the key settings you need to know to corral chat conversations, bubbles, location permissions, media controls, and the new power menu. The job of any mature OS is managing complexity and Android 11 just barely pulls it off.

snippet.title: PM Lee Hsien Loong, Pritam Singh's exchange on 'free rider' voters
snippet.description:
Singapore PM Lee Hsien Loong and Leader of the Opposition Pritam Singh had an exchange in Parliament on Wednesday (Sep 2) on appeals to vote for the opposition. "If you say: 'Vote against the Government because somebody else will look after getting the PAP Government and you just become a free rider and you vote opposition - no harm, the PAP will still be there' - then I think the system must fail, because the system can only work if people vote sincerely," said Mr Lee.

"I don't think residents in Aljunied, Hougang for 30 years and even Sengkang as a result of the last election would appreciate being called 'free riders'," said Mr Singh. Read: https://cna.asia/3lGMIr8

snippet.title: I Tried Acrylic Pour Art For The First Time
snippet.description:
Hello friends! Apologies for the long absence, but we are trying to get things back on track. No, this video didn‚Äôt take us 3 months to make - we filmed a bunch of videos in July and this is the first of them to be released! It‚Äôs not a magnum opus, just supposed to be fun and lighthearted. If you want to read more about our plans, you can check out my blog post here:

https://www.safiyasnewintrosong.com/single-post/2020/09/04/where-have-we-been

Now, onto the video! A few weeks ago, somewhere deep in a visual ASMR YouTube rabbit hole, I discovered the online acrylic pour art community - where people essentially make interesting color combos of paint in a cup, then pour that cup onto a canvas or object - and then manipulate that object to create truly mesmerizing, rainbow, psychedelic pieces of art. And I was instantly hooked - just something about the way the paints flow from the cup and then slide around the canvas really got me, ya know? So I decided to pick an acrylic pour art video and try to follow it myself, to see if I could do it too. So I chose a "pouring guru", Tiktus color art, and got to work.

What do you guys think of my ~acrylic pouring adventure~?

This video is NOT sponsored!!

Safiya's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/safiyany/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/safiyajn
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/safnygaard/

The tutorial we followed is here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yndPwAMGEgg
You can check out Tiktus‚Äôs channel here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCeAvBShy5a2_vTFflQG_zWg

snippet.title: BTS ‚Äì ‚ÄúDynamite‚Äù  (Live) | Press Play
snippet.description:
On Aug. 21, record-breaking K-pop superstars BTS achieved a new first, when they dropped their first English-language song, "Dynamite." For the latest episode of GRAMMY.com's Press Play series, the talented septet deliver a lively live performance of the sunny, disco-tinged single, complete with '70s flared pants.

"It all began from this: even in the midst of hardships, we must focus on what we can do. As for us, we found freedom and happiness in singing and dancing. This song goes to the ones who need encouragement. We hope people feel energized when listening to the song," BTS explained in a recent GRAMMY.com interview.

Read more here: https://www.grammy.com/grammys/news/bts-dynamite-interview-new-album-army.

Poikaaran un poyye solli oore kedukkaathe,
Poikaaran un poyye solli oore kedukkaathe,
Poikaaran un poyye solli oore kedukkaathe, 
Poikaaran un poyye solli oore kedukkaathe,  

Nee sollum poyyellam kekke mudiyale, 
Konjam nee nippaattu,
Unn vaaye adakke vazhi onnu irukku,
Acid'eh vaanggi oothu,

Porakkumbothe poyye vetachithan
Unne pettaanaa,
Unn appakaaran kayyile kedacha,
Vaaye naan odeppenda...

KMG Kid'du, try to make a beat'tu,
Antha beat 'tu mele mettu pottu,ettu katte paatte kettu,
motti mothi kastapattu,veette vittu paada vantha, 
Nambi vanthe naalu peru pona singapooru,
Kirukku pudichi poyi,palaye vaazhkai maranthu aadure
Nallavennu vesham pottu, nenje tookki nadakkire
Unmai kathe sollava, unnai patti sollava, 
Palagi pone paavattukku, polachi poda... naaaayyye
Kaingge kitte unne patti kettu paakkiren
Unn maanam kappal yeri matta naadu pochida,
Naan solla vanthe vaarthayellaam take note brother,
Sollaathe vaarthai vikadakavikal forever,
Poigal sollum vaaigalukku bojananggal kidayaathu,
Poyyile piranthu, poyyile valarntha - unakkelaam
Nalle saavu kidayaathu naasamattu povada,
Single singam paarada, panni koottam neenggada.

Poikaaran un poyye solli oore kedukkaathe,
Poikaaran un poyye solli oore kedukkaathe,
Poikaaran un poyye solli oore kedukkaathe, 
Poikaaran un poyye solli oore kedukkaathe,

Once upon a time was a annakaavadi,
Oore O#$&%@chathale ippe ponne saavadi
Nambe paadum inthe paattayellaam vellakaaran paadittaan,
Pesumbothu mattum vellekaaran yengge odittaan,
Nee pesum antha pechiyile ettanayo poyyi,
Athe kettu vaalum makkalukku poosure nee (nei)
English unakku teriyile, enna seriya padikkile,
Degreekoode mudikkile, oorukkithu teriyile,
Forgery mollemaari mudichevikki aatha,
Guruvukke kolaattam aadi kaatti putte buta,
Innuma adanggale unn naadagatthin aattam, 
Ini ettane pere yemaatti otte pore ottam,
Inggu solle vanthathu, rombe sogamaanathu
Manasu baaramaathu, kangal eeramaanathu,
Aanaa athe patti evanukkum kavalai ille, 
Yenaa ovvoru manushan kulleyum
Poikaaran....

Poikaaran un poyye solli oore kedukkaathe,
Poikaaran un poyye solli oore kedukkaathe,
Poikaaran un poyye solli oore kedukkaathe, 
Poikaaran un poyye solli oore kedukkaathe,

Naanum poikaaren, neeyum poikaaran,
Inthe naaripone boomiyile senthu vaalurom,
Naalumoru poyye solli, ooraye yemaatturom,
Poyye maraikke innoru poyye sollurom...

snippet.title: Novak Djokovic disqualified from US Open after hitting line judge in throat with ball | ABC News
snippet.description:
World number one Novak Djokovic has lost his fourth round match at the US Open in dramatic circumstances after he was defaulted for hitting a ball in anger that struck a female line judge in the throat.

Djokovic had just had his serve broken by Pablo Carreno Busta to trail 5-6 in the first set.

As he walked to the sideline at the change of ends, in frustration he hit the ball behind him without looking ‚Äî the line judge dropped to her knees at the back of the court, holding her neck.

After checking on the line judge and immediately apologising, the 17-time major title winner stood at the net for several minutes discussing the incident with officials including tournament referee Soeren Friemel, before going to Carreno Busta and shaking hands, then grabbing his bags and walking off court.

#NovakDjokovic #NovakDjokovicDisqualified

snippet.title: Imbestigador: BABAE, BRUTAL NA PINATAY NG SARILING BEST FRIEND DAHIL SA SELOS! | Full Episode
snippet.description:
Aired (September 5, 2020): Sa patuloy na imbestigasyon ng pulis, unti-unting nagkaroon ng linaw ang brutal na pagpatay sa 15-anyos na si Bea Claire Morri. Ang dalagang natagpuang nakabulagta, pinagsasaksak at laslas ang leeg sa isang sementeryo. Umamin si "George" kasintahan ng malapit niyang kaibigan na si Racman Panondi. Noong araw na napatay si Bea, nagkaroon sila ng pagtatalo ni Racman. Ang dahilan, pinagseselosan umano ni Racman ang biktima! Mabigyan pa kaya ng hustisiya ang dalagita?

snippet.title: I Tried Acrylic Pour Art For The First Time
snippet.description:
Hello friends! Apologies for the long absence, but we are trying to get things back on track. No, this video didn‚Äôt take us 3 months to make - we filmed a bunch of videos in July and this is the first of them to be released! It‚Äôs not a magnum opus, just supposed to be fun and lighthearted. If you want to read more about our plans, you can check out my blog post here:

https://www.safiyasnewintrosong.com/single-post/2020/09/04/where-have-we-been

Now, onto the video! A few weeks ago, somewhere deep in a visual ASMR YouTube rabbit hole, I discovered the online acrylic pour art community - where people essentially make interesting color combos of paint in a cup, then pour that cup onto a canvas or object - and then manipulate that object to create truly mesmerizing, rainbow, psychedelic pieces of art. And I was instantly hooked - just something about the way the paints flow from the cup and then slide around the canvas really got me, ya know? So I decided to pick an acrylic pour art video and try to follow it myself, to see if I could do it too. So I chose a "pouring guru", Tiktus color art, and got to work.

What do you guys think of my ~acrylic pouring adventure~?

This video is NOT sponsored!!

Safiya's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/safiyany/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/safiyajn
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/safnygaard/

The tutorial we followed is here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yndPwAMGEgg
You can check out Tiktus‚Äôs channel here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCeAvBShy5a2_vTFflQG_zWg

Via AudioNetwork

snippet.description:
‚öæ  https://www.patreon.com/smartereveryday ‚öæ
Get a Rocket City Trash Pandas shirt at http://shoptrashpandas.com/ !
Click here if you're interested in subscribing: http://bit.ly/Subscribe2SED
Behind the Scenes Video of how we built it: https://youtu.be/E60G3ba4TUA 
‚áä  Click below for more links!  ‚áä

I have been wanting to build this thing as long as I understood the physics of how it all works.  A super big thanks to David Linderman, Jeremy Fielding, Trent, and David Woodall (the welder).

I realize most people who support Smarter Every Day don't do it for "transactional" reasons, (ie, I'll support Smarter Every Day to get stuff).  I also realized that there is often a mental hurdle that must be crossed before support on Patreon starts.  My thought is that I'd really like to give folks a baseball, and it might provide enough momentum to get over that initial hurdle.  I signed the first shipment of baseballs I received, but I only have so many of those.  There's no implication that my signature is worth anything.... it's just kind of what you do with baseballs... it's a tradition.  After a certain number, it will transition to unsigned baseballs.  I've got enough signed baseballs to over all existing Patrons, and many more, but I will wait a month or so to see how many I need to get, then I'll order the second batch.  I like to support jobs and pay people for what they're good at.  The machinists and welders who made the parts in this video for example.  The whole intent here is to diversify away from solely being ad sponsored so I don't have to answer to anyone but myself and Patrons with respect to the types of content I choose to make.  Thank you for understanding what I'm doing here, and even if you decide not to kick in at https://www.patreon.com/smartereveryday , I'm super grateful you took the time to watch this video!  
Thank you very much, 

Destin

snippet.title: Android 11 review: the most important settings
snippet.description:
Android 11 is officially here. It's out for Google Pixels and even some OnePlus phones. In this review, Dieter Bohn looks at the key settings you need to know to corral chat conversations, bubbles, location permissions, media controls, and the new power menu. The job of any mature OS is managing complexity and Android 11 just barely pulls it off.
